Sometimes we get the best food at the small restaurants. I was walking with my friends on the streets of Gachibowli where I spotted this new outlet. I decided to try this place and indeed it was a very good decision.
I took parcel of Chicken 65 and Chicken Chilly and both were priced at 120RS. I would say it was a steal deal.
